00042 void CHPQuantificationDetectionFileWriterTest::WriteTest()
00043 {
00044         ParameterNameValueTypeList params;
00045         ParameterNameValueType param;
00046 
00047         CHPQuantificationDetectionData data("CHP_quantification_detection_file");
00048 
00049         data.SetAlgName(L"sig");
00050         data.SetAlgVersion(L"1.0");
00051         data.SetArrayType(L"test3");
00052         data.SetEntryCount(2, 10);
00053 
00054         param.SetName(L"an1");
00055         param.SetValueText(L"av1");
00056         params.push_back(param);
00057         data.AddAlgParams(params);
00058 
00059         params.clear();
00060         param.SetName(L"sn1");
00061         param.SetValueText(L"sv1");
00062         params.push_back(param);
00063         data.AddSummaryParams(params);
00064 
00065 
00066         CHPQuantificationDetectionFileWriter *writer = new CHPQuantificationDetectionFileWriter(data);
00067         affymetrix_calvin_data::ProbeSetQuantificationDetectionData e;
00068 
00069         writer->SeekToDataSet();
00070         e.name = "abc";
00071         e.quantification = 10.0f;
00072     e.pvalue = 0.1f;
00073         writer->WriteEntry(e);
00074         e.name = "xyz";
00075         e.quantification = 20.0f;
00076     e.pvalue = 0.2f;
00077         writer->WriteEntry(e);
00078 
00079         delete writer;
00080 
00081         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(1);
00082 
00083 
00084 
00085 
00086         CHPQuantificationDetectionData data2;
00087         CHPQuantificationDetectionFileReader reader;
00088         reader.SetFilename("CHP_quantification_detection_file");
00089         reader.Read(data2);
00090 
00091         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetAlgName() == L"sig");
00092         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetAlgVersion() == L"1.0");
00093         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetArrayType() == L"test3");
00094         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetEntryCount() == 2);
00095 
00096         ParameterNameValueTypeList p = data2.GetAlgParams();
00097         ParameterNameValueTypeList::iterator it = p.begin();
00098         param = *it;
00099         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetName() == L"an1");
00100         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetValueText() == L"av1");
00101 
00102         p = data2.GetSummaryParams();
00103         it = p.begin();
00104         param = *it;
00105         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetName() == L"sn1");
00106         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetValueText() == L"sv1");
00107 
00108 
00109         data2.GetQuantificationDetectionEntry(0, e);
00110         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(e.quantification, 10.0f, 0.0001f);
00111         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(e.pvalue, 0.10f, 0.0001f);
00112         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.name == "abc");
00113     data2.GetQuantificationDetectionEntry(1, e);
00114         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(e.quantification, 20.0f, 0.0001f);
00115         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(e.pvalue, 0.20f, 0.0001f);
00116         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.name == "xyz");
